Terms of Service for Encore Cleaner Bot

Welcome to Encore Cleaner, a Discord bot designed to automatically moderate and detect scam images in your server. By inviting or using the Encore Cleaner in your Discord server, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the Bot.
1. Acceptance of Terms
These Terms constitute a legal agreement between you and the developer of the Bot. The Bot is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. Your use of the Bot signifies your acceptance of these Terms and any future modifications.
2. Description of Service
The Bot scans messages with image attachments in your Discord server for potential scam content, such as fake Elon Musk giveaway images. If detected, it may delete the message, ban the user, save a local backup of the images for review, and send a notification. The Bot operates using local tools like Tesseract OCR and does not rely on external APIs unless explicitly configured otherwise.
3. Eligibility
You must be at least 13 years old (or the minimum age required in your jurisdiction) to use the Bot. By using the Bot, you represent that you meet this requirement and have the authority to add it to your server.
